								</extent>
								<foliation>
									<p>225 folios (+ 2 modern paper flyleaves at the beginning and at the end).</p>
								</foliation>
								<collation>
									<p>Quires (originally 23) of mostly 10 leaves each.</p>
									<p>Signatures in Hebrew letters at the beginning and at the end of quires.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>
									<p>Imperfect at the beginning and at the end.</p>
									<p>Lacuna after folio 96.</p>
								</condition>
